{"tid":2344899,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"屢次侵犯親女 六旬漢上訴得直撤強姦罪 減刑逾兩年","createTime":"2020-12-29T06:08:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T18:15:59.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5ca0b04c5d6fbb3a5d4223cdb8a67647c434e191","tid":2344899,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T06:08:45.000Z","msg":"曾有非禮智障兒媳前科的六旬漢，被揭早於十多年前曾多次非禮當時只有9歲的親女，被捕後向警察承認非禮，更以美食作比喻，「等於食嘢，好食嘅，唔會淨係食一次，會翻食」。心理學家報告形容他毫無悔意，女事主更患上嚴重抑鬱。涉案六旬漢去年初被裁定五項非禮及一項強姦罪成，遭法官李運騰判監9年3個月。他就強姦罪名提出上訴，指案中唯一強姦定罪的相關證據，與案中另外四宗事件完全一樣，但陪審團卻裁定該四案僅非禮罪成，裁決不一致。上訴庭今頒判詞，裁定上訴得直，總刑期下調至監禁7年。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201229/JK56WLJN7NDLVFQNONTTMQ22MI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201229%2FJK56WLJN7NDLVFQNONTTMQ22MI%2F&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx1iy1AgKJyIubMvfhItfpFI%3D&h=9e607f45\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201229%2FJK56WLJN7NDLVFQNONTTMQ22MI%2F&h=6f83d0f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201229/JK56WLJN7NDLVFQNONTTMQ22MI/</a>"},{"pid":"f9600c6f417f1cdb058c9c9c8f062d4562883eb3","tid":2344899,"uid":241504,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T06:18:40.000Z","msg":"等於食嘢，好食嘅，唔會淨係食一次，會翻食<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a0b9d6eb8d9a84d2d6cce454f62fb23228a5f0","tid":2344899,"uid":21545,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T06:23:15.000Z","msg":"上訴庭其實班友係咪有反社會人格障礙<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d2b4389823c2da45d32eaa8880f276c902236d","tid":2344899,"uid":253016,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T06:24:11.000Z","msg":"死廢老直接處決就得"},{"pid":"2ff6e54fb31b2f1af0ff37739281fb3a485877b5","tid":2344899,"uid":225130,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"45a0b9d6eb8d9a84d2d6cce454f62fb23228a5f0","tid":2344899,